metadata.description: Voodoo House is a generative collection that explores the concept of abstract growth and the emotional experiences that accompany transitional periods in life. Each piece in the collection is a moving digital work, accompanied by a song from Jon Waltz's upcoming EP. The visual art reflects the psychedelic aspects of the music, which come together with a mixture of techniques to make listeners feel the abstraction.
metadata.name: Voodoo House #1
